{"tid":1661473,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Tommy籲周日上街發聲","createTime":"2019-10-18T06:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T06:43:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"81691e16ce939647931ee754bdb9e69aba413755","tid":1661473,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191018/20788945\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191018%2F20788945&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=42728b42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191018%2F20788945&h=08c4e8b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191018/20788945</a><br />\n<br />\nTommy籲周日上街發聲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191018/large/1571319919_325b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191018%2Flarge%2F1571319919_325b.jpg&h=4f696767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTommy希望最終可以還彥霖一個公道。<br />\n<br />\n阮民安（Tommy）昨日到調景嶺，出席由職業訓練局青年學院學生就陳彥霖事件發起的集會，要求校方公開交代事件真相，Tommy與多位人士上台發言。Tommy表示一直有關注事件，校方昨日發公開信呼籲成立死因調查，他說：「睇到起碼校方有相應行動，亦有回應到大家嘅訴求，希望最終可以還陳同學一個公道。」<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人岑子杰前晚遇襲，Tommy相當氣憤：「咁樣只會呼籲到更加多人企出嚟。」 Tommy同時呼籲大家周日勇於站出來發聲，不要懼怕白色恐怖。特首林鄭月娥剛公佈的施政報告，他直言：「冇眼睇，今時今日仲叫人買樓。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：曹家誠<br />\n攝影：林賓尼 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【一家四口】囝囝做護士 囡囡想入行<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n鄭敬基大馬發展開公司"},{"pid":"dfd613345521bc8fd324ffa541a12497312b748a","tid":1661473,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫我推多次上熱門！<br />\n<br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去[2]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657270</a>"},{"pid":"343143c071a2d6b50608e2b7af9557f01c6bd670","tid":1661473,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:32:19.000Z","msg":"Twitter係每日必做的任務<br />\n禁兩個制都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲同我retweet哂去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日國際新聞關香港或者抵制中國事的有：<br />\nDior (向中國道歉，承認台灣係中國）<br />\n<br />\nBlizzard(共雪禁左美國大學隊賽半年，原因係美國大學隊支持Free Hong Kong)<br />\n<br />\nDreamwork（動畫畫九段線，畫出大部分的南海係屬於中國，菲律賓嚴重抗議，荷蘭海牙仲裁已經響2016裁定九段線違反聯合國國際公約，所以Dreamwork 奶共奶到洗緊細路腦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nnba (Lebron James 鬧Morey咩都唔知就亂tweet，大家可以提出任何人都唔應該響普世價值上助紂為虐、自我審查！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你響twitter大海中唔知retweet咩好<br />\ntwitter 組整左個bot<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=75fcfd09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你入    /task2</span></span><br />\n就可以搵到以上的新聞<br />\n<br />\nRetweet 加 cm ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得每日做！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你入 /task1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就可以見到人權法新聞同議員的tweet<br />\n<br />\n記得多謝埋人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc5c99e482e9ae22b13f65eca4b3e5288efe078","tid":1661473,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"01da5ace82cefdb6812c566db5482e36f426eefb","tid":1661473,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019